description: Now you have the knowledge of how to break down your opponent it is time to make the theory work in practice. Master Wong teaches you to use the unique fighting skills you have practiced. Applications can only be used in the real world if they are tested under pressure in real time. The bottom line is, you need to get fit enough, strong enough and good enough if you really want to use your Wing Chun in the real world and Master Wong can help you make this happen.
title: Wing Chun Chum Kiu - M3 Fitness - Competition
